  p229: "Ka'imi Fairbairn has been one of the most reliable and productive kickers in the league during his tenure in Houston. He enters 2025 as the top-projected kicker, benefiting from a high-scoring Texans offense.",
  p230: "Jason Myers has provided steady production as Seattle's kicker, combining accuracy with a strong leg on field goals and kickoffs. He projects as a top-tier fantasy kicker in 2025 within the Seahawks' offense.",
  p231: "Spencer Shrader is a young kicker who has shown promise in his limited NFL opportunities with the Colts. He projects as a solid fantasy option in 2025 if he can secure consistent volume in Indianapolis.",
  p232: "Brandon Aubrey burst onto the NFL scene with record-setting production, showcasing elite leg strength and range with the Cowboys. He remains a premium fantasy kicker option in 2025, though a slight projection dip suggests possible regression from his historic early career pace.",
  p233: "Zane Gonzalez has been a dependable kicker across multiple NFL stops, providing consistent fantasy production when healthy. He projects for solid output in 2025 as Atlanta's kicker in what should be a competitive offense.",
