  p240: "Chase McLaughlin has been a journeyman kicker who has provided capable production across several NFL stops. He projects as a low-end startable option in 2025 with Tampa Bay.",
  p241: "Harrison Mevis was a standout college kicker known for his powerful leg before joining the Rams. His 2025 projection suggests he can be a serviceable fantasy option in Los Angeles' offense.",
  p242: "Jake Moody was drafted by the 49ers and has shown the leg strength and accuracy that made him a college standout. In 2025 with Washington, he projects as a mid-range kicker option with a steady workload.",
  p243: "Chris Boswell has been one of the most reliable and clutch kickers in the NFL throughout his career with the Steelers. He projects as a dependable fantasy kicker in 2025, though Pittsburgh's offensive limitations may cap his ceiling.",
