  p249: "Joey Slye has been a capable NFL kicker with a strong leg, providing usable fantasy production across multiple stops. He projects as a back-end fantasy option in 2025 with the Titans.",
  p250: "Brandon McManus has been a reliable NFL kicker for over a decade, known for his strong leg and big-game performances. He projects as a modest fantasy option in 2025 with Green Bay.",
  p251: "Blake Grupe has served as a capable kicker in his NFL career, offering adequate accuracy and range. He projects as a low-end fantasy option in 2025 with the Colts.",
  p252: "Evan McPherson earned the nickname 'Money Mac' for his clutch postseason performances during Cincinnati's Super Bowl run. His 2025 projection is modest, sitting as a backend fantasy kicker with the Bengals.",
  p253: "Nick Folk has been one of the most accurate kickers in NFL history over his lengthy career. He projects as a low-end startable option in 2025 with the Jets, where his reliability provides a safe floor.",
  p254: "Wil Lutz has been a steady NFL kicker across multiple stops, known for his consistency and dependability. He projects as a back-end fantasy option in 2025 with the Broncos.",
  p255: "Graham Gano has been a reliable veteran kicker for over a decade, providing steady production throughout his career. His 2025 projection with the Giants is modest, reflecting a role as a low-upside but dependable option.",
  p256: "Riley Patterson has shown flashes of potential as a young NFL kicker across his early career. He projects as a fringe fantasy option in 2025 with the Dolphins.",
